  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.4YUjuHyUj4GkQGFn]{Weapon Group: Heavy Weapons}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">This gun is a modern rendition of the weapon once called the &ldquo;gatling gun&rdquo;, a relatively simple design with a manual or spring loaded crank for rotating the numerous barrels. The mechanism is simple, but does not have the massive firing rate or more advanced models.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The rotary cannon has no single shot option: it always fires 10 shots per attack roll.</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 64px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Rotary cannon </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 28px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">500 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 53px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1d10 piercing </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 56px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">100/400 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 39px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">65 lb. </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 138px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Auto-heavy (Special), heavy, immune, reload<br />(400 shots)</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.450g1kbvRQoe1x5P]{Auto-Heavy}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.HE1gIc0o7bZeLjFT]{Burst Fire}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.aHgsBOaLpXxmywsG]{Heavy}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.QjoW3JNAsq3eJt4s]{Reload 400 shots}</p>",
